case.title: LET LOVE LEAD - 27 (TRUST)
case.text: Good day, I am Annie Sullivan 27yrs old and i am a single lady who hopes to find true love, i hope to meet a man who is kind, caring, loving, enjoys life, one that knows there is stress in life..but doesn't let it run his life,one that isn't afraid to show and express his feelings, someone that is ready for good love relationship you can get back to me, do have a lovely day and hope to hear from you soon.
